"Testing shows the presence, not the absence, of bugs."
                                -- Edsger W. Dijkstra

git clone git://github.com/pizza/assume.git

assume is to lint as a whitelist is to a blacklist.

Goals

  * Define abstract programming language model.
  * Validate parse tree against model.
  * Detect incorrect/unsane/undefined/complex constructs.
  * Produce human-readable instructions for correcting them.
  
References

  * http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lint_(software)
  * http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blacklist_(computing)
  * http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Whitelist

